Invocation Name: waterfall sleep sounds
des:
Sounds of a trickling waterfall to put you in a deep, deep sleep. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Waterfall Sleep Sounds, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
